data.description: Welcome to the Florida resort lifestyle! Community features beach access, pools, restaurant and bar, shuffleboard, tennis and a 9-hole golf course. Unit itself has laminate wood floors, new washer and dryer, new dishwasher, brand new A/C and a marvelous garden view from your screened-in porch, a great spot to see launches from the cape as well. Only steps from the beach! assigned parking directly below unit. Excellent opportunity to begin living the beach resort life or use as an investment property.
